gridevents.desc:
This event is triggered when a cell at the end of a table is clicked. //arg1: current table object 
{
$columnIndex: 2,$rowIndex: 0,$table: VueComponent, //table component vue instance
cell,// current cell node
column:ColumnConfig, // current column information 
columnIndex: 2}
//arg2:event // native event

This event is triggered when a cell at the end of the table is right-clicked. //arg1: current table object 
{
$columnIndex: 2,$rowIndex: 0,$table: VueComponent, //table component vue instance
cell,// Current cell node
column:ColumnConfig, // Current column information 
columnIndex: 2, 
options:Array,// configuration and clearing function information
type: 'footer' //Table area type 
}
//arg2:event // native event

This event is triggered when a cell at the end of a table is double-clicked. //arg1: current table object 
{
$columnIndex: 2,$rowIndex: 0,$table: VueComponent, //table component vue instance
cell,// Current cell node
column:ColumnConfig, // Current column information 
columnIndex: 2}
//arg2:event // native event

This event is triggered when a cell in the table header is clicked. //arg1: current table object 
{
$columnIndex: 2,$rowIndex: 0,$table: VueComponent, //table component vue instance
cell,// Click the table header cell 
column:ColumnConfig, // Current column information 
columnIndex: 2,
triggerFilter:false,// Current click node filter flag 
triggerSort:false,// Current click node sorting flag}
//arg2:event // Native event

This event is triggered when a cell in the table header is right-clicked. //arg1: current table object 
{
$columnIndex: 2,$rowIndex: 0,$table: VueComponent, //table component vue instance
cell,// Current cell node
column:ColumnConfig, // Current column information 
columnIndex: 2, 
options:Array,// configuration and clearing function information
type: 'header' //Table area type 
}
//arg2:event // native event

